              </respStmt>
              <colophon>Colophon: iti śrīskaṃdapurāṇe aduḥkhanavamīkathāsamāptaḥ // cha // śake 1723 durmamati saṃvatsare nabhaśukl[e] tad dine daśamīgurūvārarāmacaṃdrasya sununā viśvanāthaparāḍakareṇa svārthaparopakarārthalikhyate // cha // śrīkṛṣṇārpaṇam astu // (f. 7v).</colophon>
